Package: OpenSourceAP.DownloadR
Title: Open Source Asset Pricing (OpenAP) Data Directly in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Tom", "Zimmermann", email = "tom.zimmermann@uni-koeln.de", role = c("cre","aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0368-5303")),
    person("Justus", "Boeker", email = "jboeker2smail.uni-koeln.de", role = "ctr"))
Description: Downloads asset returns and firm characteristics replicated from the academic asset pricing literature. The package interfaces directly with the Open Source Asset Pricing (OpenAP) project to provide convenient access to predictor portfolios, firm signals, and documentation.
